    "usability_domain": [
        "This pipeline is intended to support biomedical researchers, data scientists, and clinical informaticians interested in: Extracting true responders (true_healthy participants) from large-scale continuous glucose monitoring (CGM) datasets, Refining noisy labels (e.g., AI-READI "healthy" study group) using data-driven clustering, Classifying glucose dynamics using supervised learning (e.g., XGBoost) and time-series deep learning (e.g., Conv+BiLSTM) and Evaluating intervention efficacy or natural remission in metabolic states by detecting patterns resembling healthy glucose regulation."
    ],
